edu.brown.cs.gajith.boggle

Class Dictionary

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.gajith.boggle.Dictionary

  • public class Dictionary
extends Object
    A set of words that can be queried for membership. A Dictionary can also report whether a given string is the prefix (beginning part) of any word in the Dictionary.
    Author:
    John Jannotti

      • containsPrefix

        public boolean containsPrefix(String pref)
        Reports on whether a string is a prefix of any word in this Dictionary. A word is a prefix of itself.
        Parameters:
        pref - The string to test
        Returns:
